204 namespace internal {

209 constexpr int64_t kJulianEpochOffsetDays = INT64_C(2440588);
210 constexpr int64_t kNanosecondsPerDay = INT64_C(86400000000000);
211 
215 inline void NanosecondsToImpalaTimestamp(const int64_t nanoseconds,
216  Int96* impala_timestamp) {
217  int64_t julian_days = (nanoseconds / kNanosecondsPerDay) + kJulianEpochOffsetDays;
218  (*impala_timestamp).value[2] = (uint32_t)julian_days;
219 
220  int64_t last_day_nanos = nanoseconds % kNanosecondsPerDay;
221  int64_t* impala_last_day_nanos = reinterpret_cast<int64_t*>(impala_timestamp);
222  *impala_last_day_nanos = last_day_nanos;
223 }
224 
225 } // namespace internal
